Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
License-File: LICENSE
Requires-Dist: flamapy~=1.1.3
Requires-Dist: flamapy-fm~=1.1.3
Requires-Dist: Jinja2~=3.1.3

This package provides a variability resolution engine for UVL models and text-based implementation artifacts. It is based on Jinja2 templates and a mapping model that relates the features in the UVL model with the implementation artifacts.
